<C>__{sanchez}
<P>__{(calmly)}
<D>__{we have considered your demands very carefully, senor colon... your expectations are... excessive, in every way.}
<A>__{columbus tightens his fists, tries to remain calm.}
<C>__{columbus}
<D>__{if i am right, my requests are fair!}
<A>__{sanchez holds up a document.}
<C>__{sanchez}
<D>__{we have prepared our own contract...}
<A>__{he offers the document to columbus, who takes it, scans it quickly, shakes his head.}
<C>__{columbus}
<D>__{no...}
<C>__{sanchez}
<D>__{no?}
<C>__{columbus}
<D>__{no...! i have waited too long, fought too hard. now you expect me to take all the risks while you take the profit! no... i will not be your servant!}
